Finnish March core inflation up 0 . 1 pct yr / yr . Finnish core inflation rose 0 . 4 percent in March on February for a year - on - year rise of 0 . 1 percent , Statistics Finland said in a statement on Thursday . The mean of five economists ' forecasts for the March core inflation rate had been a 0 . 3 percent rise in a 0 . 2 - 0 . 4 percent range . The Bank of Finland ' s target for the year - on - year change in the underlying rate of inflation - - its chief gauge for monetary policy - - is a rise of no more than around two percent . - - Helsinki newsroom + 358 - 9 - 680 50 245 , news @ reuters . fi 
